    "The more hierarchical the network, the more deterioration occurs due to the high centralization.",
    "To mislead the opponent, it is necessary to facilitate organized communication between team members while maintaining the appearance of disorganization 24.",
    "Among other things, the communication and passing network layers of the network contribute to the success of the team.",
    "The evaluation of patterns in the multilayer network of a team may be relevant to estimate the success of the cooperation.",
    "Our goal was to develop a series of machine learning steps that determine the most important predictors of the outcome variable from information obtained from multilayer network connection conditions and organizational, operational characteristics."
